# DATABASE RELATIONS

All IDs must be auto-generated by MongoDB.

Users must NEVER manually input relation IDs.

System must automatically create and manage references.

Use proper ObjectId references.

Example:

Student -> Class
Student -> Family
Teacher -> Subject
Class -> Teacher
Exam -> Subject
Result -> Student + Exam

All relationships must be validated.

